org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors
Class AeInlinePropertyAliasVisitor

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.AeAbstractDefVisitor
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.AeInlinePropertyAliasVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeDefVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
AeWSBPELInlinePropertyAliasVisitor
public class AeInlinePropertyAliasVisitor
extends AeAbstractDefVisitor

Visits the def to inline usage of property alias's where possible. This will reduce the overhead of having to search for these prop aliases at runtime.
